         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="panel" href="#collapse7" target="self">
        <div aria-expanded="false" class="panel-heading" id="panel7">
         <h4 class="panel-title">
          <span class="plus_sym">
           <img height="20" src="../images/structure/plus.svg" width="20"/>
          </span>
          Know why you lead
         </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapse7">
         <div class="panel-body top_body">
          <div>
           <p>
            Can leadership be taught? Yes, most anyone can learn a set of skills. But it takes one key ingredient to complete the recipe.
           </p>
           <p>
            When you understand your motivations, you will:
           </p>
           <ul>
            <li>
             Lead with a sense of personal mission.
            </li>
            <li>
             Inspire others with your passion and purpose.
            </li>
            <li>
             Mobilize others to action.
            </li>
           </ul>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="panel-body bottom_body">
          <div>
           <p>
            At the Center for Leadership, you will uncover your passion to lead out of who you are.
           </p>
           <a class="button learn-more">
            Learn More
           </a>
           <div class="learn-content">
            <p>
             <a href="../undergraduates/academic-certificate-courses.html" title="Learn more about the Undergraduate Leadership Certificate">
              Certificate Program for Undergrads
             </a>
             <a href="../phd-students/fellowship-in-leadership.html" title="Learn more about the Fellowship in Leadership">
              <br/>
              Fellowship in Leadership for Grads &amp; Staff
             </a>
             <br/>
             <a href="../work-with-us/consulting.html" title="Learn more about Consulting">
              Consulting for Northwestern Students, Faculty, Departments and Programs
              <br/>
             </a>
             <a href="../work-with-us/consulting.html" title="Learn more about Consulting">
              <br/>
             </a>
            </p>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="panel" href="#collapse8" target="self">
        <div aria-expanded="false" class="panel-heading" id="panel8">
         <h4 class="panel-title">
          <span class="plus_sym">
           <img height="20" src="../images/structure/plus.svg" width="20"/>
          </span>
          Build resilience through risk and failure
         </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="collapse8">
         <div class="panel-body top_body">
          <div>
           <p>
            Is success just the absence of failure? Most leaders say they learn more from failures than from successes.
           </p>
           <p>
            When you understand how to manage risks as a leader, you will:
           </p>
           <ul>
            <li>
             Learn from setbacks.
            </li>
            <li>
             Embrace failure as an opportunity to become more resilient.
            </li>
            <li>
             Open the door to true innovation.
            </li>
           </ul>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="panel-body bottom_body">
          <div>
           <p>
            At the Center for Leadership, you will build resilience and grow through adversity.
           </p>
           <a class="button learn-more">
            Learn More
           </a>
           <div class="learn-content">
            <p>
             <a href="../undergraduates/coaching.html" title="Learn more about Coaching for Undergrads">
              Coaching for Undergrads
             </a>
